snippet.textDisplay: I have called Mianwali home for a decade in my life. On my bus journeys home from Islamabad/Lahore it was always Attaullah  Esakhelvi songs that were played. Its great that he was finally invited to Coke Studio. He has given his life to music and his fans adore him though social media reduced him to truck song memes. I hope there are more songs of him this season. And i hope he pushes the boundaries of what he has done in the past and experiments during his stint with Coke Studio.
